      "content": "but that's just it... there's nothing to \"help.\" the person you're talking to isn't even real, it's just a script i've memorized to make everyone else comfortable. even if i talked to a professional, i'd just be performing as \"a patient.\" it feels like there's a void where my life should be. it's like i'm already gone, just waiting for my body to catch up.",
